## Useful Bash Commands

#### Shortcuts

- **`Tab`** - Auto-complete files and folder names
- **`Ctrl + A`** - Go to beginning of line
- **`CTRL + E`** - Go to end of line 

#### Core Demands

- **`cd`** - Home directory
- **`ls`** - Short listing
- **`clear`** - Clear screen

#### Directory Management

- **`mkdir`** - Create new directory
- **`rmdir`** - Remove directory
